           TESTSUITE 'DEMONSTRATE UNIT TESTING A CALLED SUBPROGRAM' 

      *****************************************************************
      * UNIT TESTS TO DEMONSTRATE MOCKING FEATURES OF ZUTZCPC.
      *****************************************************************  

           TESTCASE 'IT RETURNS VALUE A TO THE CALLER'
           PERFORM 1000-RETURN-VALUE-A
           EXPECT LS-ARG-2 TO BE 'This is value A'    

           TESTCASE 'IT RETURNS VALUE B TO THE CALLER'
           PERFORM 1000-RETURN-VALUE-A
           EXPECT LS-ARG-2 TO BE 'This is value A'    

